<p>For JSON text:</p>

<p><strong><code>application/json</code></strong></p>

<blockquote>
  <p>The MIME media type for JSON text is <strong><code>application/json</code></strong>. The default encoding is UTF-8. (Source: <a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc4627.txt" rel="noreferrer">RFC 4627</a>).</p>
</blockquote>

<p>For <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JSONP" rel="noreferrer">JSONP</a> (runnable javascript) with callback:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p><strong><code>application/javascript</code></strong></p>
</blockquote>

